---
import siteData from "../data/site-data.json";
import logoImage from "../assets/logo.png";
---

<footer class="bg-ink text-paper pt-16 pb-12 border-t-2 border-ink">
  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-12"
  >
    <!-- 左：ロゴとサブタイトル -->
    <div class="space-y-2">
      <a
        href="#"
        class="inline-block group focus:outline-none"
        aria-label="HaveASite."
      >
        <img
          src={logoImage.src}
          alt="HaveASite."
          width="120"
          height="22"
          class="h-7 md:h-8 w-auto object-contain invert hue-rotate-180"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </a>
      <p class="text-xs text-paper/60 tracking-widest font-serif leading-relaxed pt-1">
        あなたのお店の魅力をカタチに。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 中：ナビゲーションリンク -->
    <div class="space-y-4 md:max-w-[200px] md:mx-auto w-full">
      <h3
        class="font-serif font-bold text-sm tracking-wider text-accent border-b border-paper/10 pb-2"
      >
        MENU
      </h3>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-sm text-paper/80">
        {
          siteData.navigation.map((item) => (
            <li>
              <a
                href={item.url}
                class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-200 block py-1"
              >
                {item.label}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- 右：お問い合わせ・ご相談 -->
    <div class="space-y-4 md:max-w-[280px] md:ml-auto w-full">
      <h3
        class="font-serif font-bold text-sm tracking-wider text-accent border-b border-paper/10 pb-2"
      >
        CONTACT
      </h3>
      <p class="text-xs text-paper/60 leading-relaxed">
        ホームページ無料サンプルのご相談は、フォームまたは公式LINEより承っております。まずはお気軽にご連絡ください。
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-2 pt-2 flex flex-col items-center md:items-stretch">
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="block w-full max-w-[280px] text-center bg-terracotta text-paper font-serif font-bold text-[11px] tracking-widest py-2 hover:bg-paper hover:text-ink transition-colors duration-300 border border-paper"
        >
          フォームから相談する
        </a>
        <a
          href={siteData.contact.lineUrl}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="block w-full max-w-[280px] text-center bg-[#06C755] text-paper font-serif font-bold text-[11px] tracking-widest py-2 hover:bg-paper hover:text-[#06C755] transition-colors duration-300 border border-[#06C755]"
        >
          LINEから相談する
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- フッターボトム -->
  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 pt-8 border-t border-paper/10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between text-xs text-paper/40"
  >
    <div class="flex space-x-6 mb-4 sm:mb-0">
      <a
        href="/privacy-policy"
        class="hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-200"
      >
        プライバシーポリシー
      </a>
    </div>
    <p>&copy; 2026 HaveASite. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</footer>
